description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Last week one of the wildest cases was brought forward on the Internet involving a man who was driving while attending court for driving with a suspended license. The following days led to a rollercoaster of new information now leading up to the fact that this individual never even had a license to begin with. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The “Suspended License” Guy Lied The Whole Time...
